nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Dr Person1,  At my last visit I asked if it would be safe for me to get a whooping cough shot (as well as a flu shot) while taking Ibrance and my other meds? You were going to check with the pharmacist. Did they respond back? If it is ok can I have those shots at LOCATION? Thank you  Person2
